This is why you may notice some of your neighbours have power, but you don't. It is normal to see 1 in 3 homes affected. Engineers have arrived in the area. They are working hard to fix the problem and will get your power back on as quickly as possible. At this stage, we're aiming to have your power back on by . If this changes, we'll let you know.
